spec_data.Name: libgovirt
spec_data.Description:
libgovirt is a library that allows applications to use oVirt REST API
to list VMs managed by an oVirt instance, and to get the connection
parameters needed to make a SPICE/VNC connection to them.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 11 Sep 2017 03:06:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A GObject library for interacting with oVirt REST API
